description: The Porsche Vision Gran Turismo is unmistakably a Porsche, but one that features future-orientated versions of familiar Porsche design elements. Some of the standout design details include the sporty height-to-width ratio, an extremely low-set bonnet and very pronounced wings. At the front, the lights and the integrated air intakes share a similar design language with the Taycan, while at the rear the narrow light strip is a development of that found on 911 and Taycan models.
creator: Bnuuy
